title: Ep - 86 - CHLOE TRAUTMAN FROM SIESTA KEY
description:
Last season on Siesta Key Chloe Trautman was the victim of body shaming by male cast members. In this interview she discusses how she dealt with it on and off the show, whether she is secretly in love with Alex, the impact of sudden fame, and what we can expect from this season. 


Patrick Waites, a band promoter from Austin, Texas reviews this week’s episode of Vanderpump Rules and gives his assessment of the relationship between James and Logan. 


Stephen McGee from Summer House explains what it was like living in the Hamptons all summer long with Carl, Kyle, and his girlfriend Amanda and the horrible décor of the home’s outdated kitchen.
